title: NFL ATL: Who's winning training camp battles?
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Who's winning training camp battles?
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- highlight the latest news from around the NFL and debate who wins the top training camp position battles. Plus, Wesseling unveils the top backup quarterbacks in the league.
